@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_cfsdzi(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = ((0.27 * (v0 + 0.92 * tmp + 0.60)) / (wp.abs(v0 + 0.29) + (v1 + 0.34 - v0 + 0.43)))
    v1 = ((v1 * wp.abs(v2 + 0.80)) + tmp)
    v0 = 1.00
    v0 = (wp.cos(wp.exp(v0 + 0.51)) / 0.83)
    tmp = v0
    v2 = 0.54
    v2 = 0.99
    data[tid] = v0
